\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {9}{\ignorespaces Category-level performance heatmap. Swallow-8B maintains consistently high scores across all categories (darker green). Qwen2.5-7B struggles particularly on Design, Maintenance-Sabo, and Comparative/Cross-Cutting queries, which require cross-referencing multiple standards---a task where Japanese continual pre-training provides clear advantages.}}{11}{figure.caption.25}\protected@file@percent }
